Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.10,0:00:13.85,main,Supervisor,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you must be Ohkuma Minoru-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.35,0:00:21.43,main,Supervisor,0000,0000,0000,,Most of the other students will start \Nmoving into the dorm tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.43,0:00:24.28,main,Supervisor,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you a quick tour of \Nthe facilities today, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.28,0:00:28.76,main,Supervisor,0000,0000,0000,,Get some rest for now. \NYou must be awfully tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.76,0:00:29.58,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.46,0:00:46.55,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.52,0:00:52.52,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,A tiger beetle. It's even \Nprettier than the picture!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.73,0:00:56.52,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,A peacock butterfly, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.52,0:00:57.93,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen one before!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.50,0:01:06.56,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.92,0:01:25.19,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.93,0:01:25.18,sign_2013_19_Self_introductio,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(315,90)\fsp6}Self-introductions
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.12,0:01:30.69,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Akebi Komichi, seat number 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.41,0:03:07.95,sign_3520_34_Episode_One__The,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(482,1)\fs14\pos(525,75)}Episode Five \NI Want to Learn Lots
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.52,0:03:09.95,main,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,A ladybug?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.95,0:03:11.49,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,It's a weevil.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.49,0:03:13.71,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Their long necks make them unique.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.71,0:03:15.29,main,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.29,0:03:17.47,italics,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,Akebi Komichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.81,0:03:24.47,italics,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,Last time, she had a Schlegel's \Ngreen tree frog.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.72,0:03:29.26,italics,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,And today, she's playing with a weevil.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.48,0:03:34.36,main,Student,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.36,0:03:35.53,main,Student,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.03,0:03:41.91,main,Girl1,0000,0000,0000,,No way, no way! I can't \Nstand this sort of thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.91,0:03:44.03,main,Girl2,0000,0000,0000,,Should I go get a teacher ASAP?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.37,0:03:45.71,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,A Japanese rat snake.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.17,0:03:51.41,main,Girl3,0000,0000,0000,,It looked this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.41,0:03:53.03,main,Girl4,0000,0000,0000,,It's gonna bite you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.33,0:03:55.09,italics,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,It's not even scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.15,0:03:57.42,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,Are you lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.63,0:03:59.55,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.37,0:04:03.05,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Ohkuma Minoru-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.88,0:04:05.79,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.25,0:04:09.62,italics,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,She has eyes like a seal's.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.62,0:04:13.30,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take it somewhere quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.80,0:04:16.59,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... Let's.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.47,0:04:28.60,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,This area should be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.19,0:04:34.93,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Ohkuma-san, is that your own cage?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.93,0:04:37.21,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,You actually bring it to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.21,0:04:40.72,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Because you never know \Nwhat you'll find, or where!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.34,0:04:47.23,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,Japanese rat snakes are interesting \Nbecause their colors and patterns vary
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.23,0:04:48.48,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,depending on the region.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.48,0:04:51.09,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, really?! I never knew that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.59,0:04:55.10,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen them swimming like \Npros in the river before!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.10,0:04:56.79,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,That's a priceless sighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.79,0:04:59.65,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,And not long ago, \Nwhen I was walking in the woods,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.65,0:05:02.42,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I bumped into a vine \Nwrapped around a branch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.10,0:05:05.14,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,And that vine was...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.14,0:05:06.73,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.55,0:05:10.49,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,A Japanese rat snake!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.49,0:05:11.91,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,Incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.88,0:05:16.67,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,What's that, Ohkuma-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.67,0:05:18.25,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,My research notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.25,0:05:20.57,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,I write down unique characteristics \Nof living things I see,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.57,0:05:23.68,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,and the details of how \NI found them, every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.17,0:05:27.08,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,Your stories gave me valuable information.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.55,0:05:28.91,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I do that, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.77,0:05:34.72,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I always write down things \NI notice in a notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.40,0:05:38.56,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,So you're also interested in the \Nobservation of living things?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.98,0:05:39.06,sign_8133_69_Class_1_3,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-15.66\pos(581,228)}Class 1-3
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.03,0:05:39.85,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.06,0:05:39.19,sign_8133_69_Class_1_3,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(495,143)}Class 1-3
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.19,0:05:40.56,sign_8133_69_Class_1_3,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-11.95\pos(510,165)}Class 1-3
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.96,0:05:43.03,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,Class 1-3?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.06,0:05:47.59,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I write notes about everyone in our class.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.59,0:05:51.27,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I was just so happy to have classmates, \Nsince I've never had them before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.83,0:05:59.83,sign_8133_69_Class_1_3,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\bord4\fs21}Class 1-3
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.09,0:05:55.86,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I want to learn lots \Nabout everyone... but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.53,0:05:59.84,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I can't always find the right \Ntiming to talk to them, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.84,0:06:02.68,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,That's where observation comes in handy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.97,0:06:07.38,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,Learning more about someone, \Nsuch as what they like and dislike,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.38,0:06:10.13,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,could help you out in future conversations.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.25,0:06:12.88,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's do that together!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.48,0:06:15.46,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
