Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.52,0:06:21.47,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,According to my observations,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.47,0:06:24.48,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,our subject appears right \Nhere every morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.39,0:06:29.34,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Hiraiwa Hotaru-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.34,0:06:32.44,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't really talked \Nto her very much yet.
