Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.70,0:07:13.79,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,This is truly intriguing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.64,0:07:16.82,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,Akebi-san?
