Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.67,0:07:36.26,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.36,0:07:41.56,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I do that for my little sister a lot, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.92,0:07:44.14,main,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.14,0:07:46.40,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're very welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.91,0:07:53.81,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do that, Akebi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.81,0:07:54.65,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.07,0:07:56.59,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,Observing living things means
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.59,0:08:00.33,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,watching them from an objective \Nviewpoint and recording what you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.33,0:08:02.76,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,You're not supposed to interfere \Nin what you observe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.76,0:08:05.28,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.48,0:08:10.87,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,It's so shiny...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.57,0:08:15.55,italics,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,I got some interesting data.\N Akebi Komichi is...
