Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.19,0:08:22.82,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Hotaru-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.12,0:08:26.08,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,You finally succeeded in \Nyour challenge? Way to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.44,0:08:30.65,main,Hotaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll work hard so I can buy \Nit on my own next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.07,0:08:34.89,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,You could call it spying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.89,0:08:39.22,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,You erase your own presence in order \Nto secretly observe your subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.22,0:08:41.54,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,To ensure you don't miss \Neven a moment's change...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.54,0:08:44.41,main,Hitomi,0000,0000,0000,,What did you call me out here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.76,0:09:02.66,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Washio Hitomi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.50,0:09:05.76,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,She's talking to a girl from Class 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.76,0:09:07.50,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.50,0:09:09.93,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,I live in the Mangetsu Dorm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.78,0:09:17.31,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like they're \Ntalking about something,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.31,0:09:19.17,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,but I can't hear them from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.17,0:09:22.53,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,It's not just their conversation \Nthat can tell us what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.53,0:09:26.50,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,Let's carefully observe their body language, \Nexpressions, and the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.72,0:09:28.70,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Stare...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.99,0:09:30.93,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,Stare...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.97,0:09:38.90,main,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,What could they be talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.38,0:09:40.86,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nawashiro-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.86,0:09:42.18,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,Shh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.04,0:09:46.70,main,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,It's always so easy to \Ntell where Akebi-chan is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.77,0:09:51.56,main,Hitomi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. I can hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.66,0:09:55.83,main,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,Heya, Hitomi-chan... and...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.08,0:09:58.58,main,Mihoshi,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.40,0:10:02.46,main,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, Tanabe-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.46,0:10:05.08,main,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, was I interrupting?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.58,0:10:09.79,main,Hitomi,0000,0000,0000,,No, actually, this is perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.79,0:10:12.36,main,Hitomi,0000,0000,0000,,She says she wants to \Nbe your friend, Yasuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.70,0:10:13.76,main,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.82,0:10:15.62,main,Hitomi,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.24,0:10:18.47,main,Hitomi,0000,0000,0000,,Just what were you two doing?
