Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.70,0:10:33.24,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, Ohkuma-san, did we really need \Nto hide ourselves {\i1}this{\i0} well?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.24,0:10:35.93,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,You stand out no matter where you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.93,0:10:39.90,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,so we might as well conceal ourselves \Nfrom our subject completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.30,0:10:42.00,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.76,0:10:47.40,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, here comes someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.40,0:10:48.99,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,It's Shijou Riona-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.99,0:10:56.40,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see very well from in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.75,0:11:00.89,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,Is she searching for something?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.72,0:11:14.76,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.78,0:11:20.04,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,A sandwich?! That looks so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.51,0:11:23.73,main,Riona,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's just, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.73,0:11:26.91,main,Riona,0000,0000,0000,,I missed breakfast today \Nbecause I overslept,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.91,0:11:29.07,main,Riona,0000,0000,0000,,so my mom wrapped this up for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.91,0:11:33.29,main,Riona,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Ohkuma-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.38,0:11:38.60,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm so sorry!
