Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.97,0:11:49.55,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't going very well, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.82,0:11:53.93,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,But I've still been able to gather \Nsome very interesting data,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.93,0:11:55.32,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,so it all worked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.31,0:12:03.60,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you're really good \Nat drawing, Ohkuma-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.63,0:12:08.01,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,S-Since I keep a research \Nnotebook every day,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.01,0:12:10.32,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,I naturally picked up the ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.32,0:12:12.07,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,That's so impressive!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.71,0:12:13.99,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.34,0:12:16.33,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,Are you finished drawing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.76,0:12:21.06,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.06,0:12:22.66,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,Drawing it in a simplified manner
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.66,0:12:26.56,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,can actually enhance the subject's \Nunique characteristics.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.35,0:12:28.71,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,Another good call.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.99,0:12:41.11,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,That feels nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.11,0:12:43.82,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's a very nice breeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.82,0:12:46.61,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,Since we're always stuck at \Nour desks during class time,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.61,0:12:50.37,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,we're lucky to have a chance to \Nobserve in this kind of setting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.86,0:12:52.12,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.40,0:12:56.63,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,You get a better look at people's hobbies, \Npreferences, and natural behaviors.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.04,0:12:59.60,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,For example... let me see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.98,0:13:01.00,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,Look there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.88,0:13:05.36,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,Togano Mai-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.61,0:13:12.20,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that she can draw so many \Ndifferent species of birds so distinctly
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.20,0:13:14.56,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,tells me that she's very fond of birds.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.56,0:13:15.64,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.16,0:13:18.86,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,I hope I can have a good \Nchat with her sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.49,0:13:22.99,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,Minakami Riri-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.31,0:13:25.29,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Is she done drawing, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.29,0:13:28.62,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's more likely that she's \Nlooking for something to draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.62,0:13:31.11,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,The way she patiently searches for prey
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.11,0:13:33.76,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,reminds me of a black leopard, \Na master of hunting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.02,0:13:37.38,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.65,0:13:42.12,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,Or... maybe she just doesn't like \Nbig crowds of people, like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.70,0:14:17.61,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,You've spent a lot of time watching \Neveryone, huh, Ohkuma-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.61,0:14:18.62,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.86,0:14:21.36,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,I-I wouldn't say "everyone"...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.36,0:14:23.87,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,The living thing that currently \Ninterests me the most is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.62,0:14:25.87,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Is?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.22,0:14:29.57,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.88,0:14:37.35,main,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,Akebi-san, there you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.35,0:14:39.91,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ohkuma-san, you're really\N good at drawing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.91,0:14:41.24,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,She really is!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.64,0:14:43.86,main,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you captured its unique \Ncharacteristics really well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.60,0:14:49.51,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, Ohkuma-san, you're red as an apple.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.53,0:14:52.03,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,An apple!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.13,0:14:52.36,main,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.36,0:14:53.73,main,Komichi; Touko; Erika,0000,0000,0000,,How cute!
