Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.96,0:15:02.96,sign_8133_69_Class_1_3,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz24.47\pos(514,149)\c&H71706B&\fs20}Roubai Academy 5
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.60,0:15:07.73,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,Akebi-san, didn't something feel \Nstrange to you a moment ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.73,0:15:08.87,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Strange how?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.87,0:15:10.71,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,Like someone was watching us...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.96,0:15:15.38,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.31,0:15:20.16,main,Touko,0000,0000,0000,,So yeah, that happened. \NI laughed my butt off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.16,0:15:21.61,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.73,0:15:29.25,italics,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it. The one watching was \Nmy roommate, Tougeguchi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.95,0:15:37.99,italics,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea there was \Nsomeone else like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.81,0:15:39.99,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.35,0:15:41.54,main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.97,0:15:46.49,italics,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,But why would...
