Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.76,0:15:52.51,sign_22766_273_Akebi_Komichi,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord1\pos(357,280)\frz355.8}Akebi Komichi
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.52,0:15:59.67,main,Ayumi,0000,0000,0000,,Today was another bust.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.14,0:16:01.96,main,Ayumi,0000,0000,0000,,I just never get the chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.65,0:16:06.44,main,Ayumi,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, an elite all-girls \Nschool in the country
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.44,0:16:09.21,main,Ayumi,0000,0000,0000,,should be full o' girls \Nwho ain't that popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.21,0:16:14.41,main,Ayumi,0000,0000,0000,,But they're all so pretty, and they're \Nalways with their brilliant buddies...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.74,0:16:17.88,main,Ayumi,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was the only one on her side!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.88,0:16:19.90,main,Ayumi,0000,0000,0000,,Akebi Komichi, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.41,0:16:26.37,main,Ayumi,0000,0000,0000,,traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.64,0:16:32.67,main,Ayumi,0000,0000,0000,,Man, nothin' makes me feel \Nbetter than a good scream!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.85,0:16:41.65,main,Ayumi,0000,0000,0000,,Akebi...san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.65,0:16:43.94,main,Ayumi,0000,0000,0000,,And... Ohkuma-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.94,0:16:45.73,main,Ayumi,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, th-this ain't what it looks like!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.73,0:16:50.29,main,Ayumi,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't sayin' anything about you, \NAkebi-san... um... I mean, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.47,0:16:52.35,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.72,0:17:21.12,flashback,Ayumi,0000,0000,0000,,Why's a pretty girl like her hafta \Ntake the test for this school?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.76,0:17:24.54,flashback,Ayumi,0000,0000,0000,,It's gonna kill my middle school debut.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.89,0:17:26.14,flashback,Ayumi,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.20,0:17:30.87,flashback,Ayumi,0000,0000,0000,,What am I gonna do if this doesn't \Nget better before the exam?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.86,0:17:36.40,flashback italics,Ayumi,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot my handkerchief...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.76,0:17:38.07,flashback italics,Ayumi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.87,0:17:45.57,flashback,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.15,0:17:47.34,flashback,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Use this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.44,0:17:55.50,flashback,Ayumi,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.50,0:17:57.82,flashback,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you using a restroom \Nso far from everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.82,0:18:00.34,flashback,Ayumi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Er... What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.56,0:18:04.10,flashback,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I just feel kinda uneasy in crowded places.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.45,0:18:06.86,flashback,Ayumi,0000,0000,0000,,There is a god...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.68,0:18:09.04,flashback,Ayumi,0000,0000,0000,,A kind one...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.36,0:18:13.10,sign_22766_273_Akebi_Komichi,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H96B477&\bord1\fs40\pos(330,240)\frz2.226}Akebi Komichi
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.74,0:18:13.10,flashback,Ayumi,0000,0000,0000,,"Akebi Komichi."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.10,0:18:15.83,flashback italics,Announcement,0000,0000,0000,,The exam will begin shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.39,0:18:17.82,flashback,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta run!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.42,0:18:19.11,flashbackitalicstop,Announcement,0000,0000,0000,,Please report to your designated classroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.82,0:18:19.11,flashback,Ayumi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.93,0:18:22.37,flashback,Ayumi,0000,0000,0000,,What d'ya want me to do with this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.29,0:18:25.21,flashback,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it until the next time I see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.58,0:18:33.09,flashback,Ayumi,0000,0000,0000,,Next time? What does she mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.43,0:18:35.95,flashback,Ayumi,0000,0000,0000,,This is just the entrance exam venue.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.95,0:18:37.77,flashback,Ayumi,0000,0000,0000,,There's no guarantee we'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.00,0:18:41.08,flashback,Ayumi,0000,0000,0000,,Was she tellin' me I have to pass?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.31,0:18:45.93,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,This is the handkerchief \NI lent to you before the exam!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.99,0:18:49.40,main,Ayumi,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.40,0:18:51.94,main,Ayumi,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to return it all this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.21,0:18:56.43,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.74,0:18:59.62,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,So that girl was you, Tougeguchi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.62,0:19:02.09,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,All this time, I wondered who it was!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.09,0:19:04.79,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy we got into \Nthis school together!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.79,0:19:05.97,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.08,0:19:12.84,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I just didn't recognize you in the uniform.\N It makes you look so different.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.40,0:19:18.22,italics,Ayumi,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought the girl in the silly PJs
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.22,0:19:21.49,italics,Ayumi,0000,0000,0000,,would show up in a sailor uniform \Non the first day, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.66,0:19:30.68,italics,Ayumi,0000,0000,0000,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.04,0:19:36.55,italics,Ayumi,0000,0000,0000,,It's because I met Akebi-san and realized \Nsomeone else was as nervous as me
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.55,0:19:38.47,italics,Ayumi,0000,0000,0000,,that I was able to stick with the exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.43,0:19:42.82,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do now, Ohkuma-san? \NThe subject caught us again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.24,0:19:45.90,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,At this point, you might \Nas well call it a talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.84,0:19:52.54,main,Ayumi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm gonna go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.54,0:19:53.36,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.53,0:19:58.60,main,Ayumi,0000,0000,0000,,Akebi Komichi...san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.53,0:20:01.94,main,Ayumi,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.60,0:20:05.45,main,Ayumi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad to know ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.65,0:20:10.97,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Same to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.57,0:20:28.48,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,I guess Tougeguchi-san was looking for the \Nright moment to talk to you all along, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.75,0:20:32.25,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,She should have said something to me sooner!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.63,0:20:42.21,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,There were some blunders and \Naccidents along the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.21,0:20:46.04,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,but I guess we can say our observation \Nmission was an overall success.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.04,0:20:47.12,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.12,0:20:51.13,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I was really happy to learn some \Nnew things about our classmates!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.81,0:20:53.00,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.77,0:20:57.76,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought I'd have a chance \Nto talk to you this way,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.76,0:21:01.54,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,so observing with you has been \Na great experience for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.42,0:21:03.52,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,So I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.45,0:21:06.27,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,want to thank you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.01,0:21:09.41,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.10,0:21:14.95,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I always wanted a chance to \Ntalk to you, too, Ohkuma-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.53,0:21:16.28,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.52,0:21:22.33,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,I wondered why you were always \Nsecretly watching me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.15,0:21:25.93,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Y-You knew about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.31,0:21:31.14,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,But I got to learn lots of things \NI didn't know about you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.14,0:21:34.44,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,You know a lot about living things, \Nand you're good at drawing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.02,0:21:39.67,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,There's still a lot I don't know,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.67,0:21:42.20,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,so I hope you'll teach me \Nlots more from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.27,0:21:57.24,main,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to observe \Ninsects together next time?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.65,0:22:02.13,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.49,0:22:07.21,main,Komichi,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.22,0:22:07.90,top,Minoru,0000,0000,0000,,Akebi-san, not so tight...
